%h1.title Create a new account
%p Give the group a descriptive name, like "home" or "business", then you'll invite people to join the account who can make labels.
= simple_form_for @account, :html => { :class => 'form-horizontal' } do |f|
  = f.input :name, autofocus: true
  = f.button :submit, "Create account", :class => 'is-primary'
